title: ArkansasVarsity.com Week Five Weekly Blitz
text:
ArkansasVarsity.com Week Five Weekly Blitz Luke Matheson & Jason Kilburn CLICK HERE TO SUBSCRIBE TO ARKANSASVARSITY.COM 
We are now in week five of the 2015 Arkansas high school football season, and there are several great games taking place this week. 
ArkansasVarsity.com publisher Luke Matheson and recruiting analyst Jason Kilburn take a look at several top games this week, discuss recruiting, teams to watch. We also break down last week's match ups between Greenwood and Van Buren, and Hot Springs Lakeside and Camden Fairview. 
We discuss several athletes from across the state to include Sheridan running back Brockton Brown and lineman Jacob Atnip , Lakeside running back Colt Housley , wide receiver Maurice Bradford , and quarterback Fisher Alexander, Ft Smith Northside offensive lineman Will Clements , Greenwood quarterback Luke Hales , Star City lineman Austin Capps , and more. 
Additionally, we will visit once again with Steve Gray, founder of the Gray's Power Poll - a comprehensive ranking and prediction system for high school football. 
You can listen to this week's podcast in the audio player below.
